content:
Skills-based routing isn't supported for external routing.
Skills-based routing doesn't support Voice Calls.
Skills-based routing doesn't support estimated wait time.
These types of transfers aren't supported for chat:
Transfer from a queue to a skill
Transfer from a skill to a queue, unless you're transferring chats from a Service Chat and Embedded Chat standard channel
Transfer from a skill directly to a user or button
title: Skills-Based Routing Limitations in Service Cloud
